Package com.advertisementproject.zuulgateway.Swagger

Class SwagResourcesConfig

java.lang.Object
com.advertisementproject.zuulgateway.Swagger.SwagResourcesConfig
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.function.Supplier<java.util.List<springfox.documentation.swagger.web.SwaggerResource>>, springfox.documentation.swagger.web.SwaggerResourcesProvider
@Component
@Primary
public class SwagResourcesConfig
extends java.lang.Object
implements springfox.documentation.swagger.web.SwaggerResourcesProvider
Swagger resources configuration that aggregates swagger documentation for all services by fetching their api docs. Swagger API documentation for all services can be viewed at "http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui/".

    • swaggerResource

      private springfox.documentation.swagger.web.SwaggerResource swaggerResource​(java.lang.String name, java.lang.String routeName)
      Factory method to build a SwaggerResource using display name for the drop-down list, location of the api docs for the service and also declares Swagger version.
      Parameters:
      name - the name of the service to appear in the drop-down list at "http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui/"
      routeName - the route name for the service to build a SwaggerResource for.
      Returns:
      SwaggerResource that allows showing Swagger api documentation for a service
